<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Buzón UPV</h1>
    <p>Hola <%= @suggestion.author %>, hemos recibido una petición para eliminar la sugerencia "<%= @suggestion.title %>"</p>
    <p>Si deseas eliminar la sugerencia de forma definitiva haz click en el siguiente enlace. En caso contrario ignora este email.</p>
    <%= link_to 'Eliminar sugerencia', @url %>
    <p>Gracias por utilizar el Buzón UPV</p>
    <br>
    <p>--------------------------------------------------------------</p>
    <br>
    <h1>Mailbox UPV</h1>
    <p>Hi <%= @suggestion.author %>, We have received a request to remove the suggestion "<%= @suggestion.title %>"</p>
    <p>If you want to delete this suggestion permanently, click on the link below. Otherwise ignore this email.</p>
    <%= link_to 'Delete suggestion', @url %>
    <p>Thanks for using the Mailbox UPV</p>
  </body>
</html>
